  m_text: Guide each arrow out of the board by clearing its path. Each arrow can
    only escape in the direction its head is pointing. Tap an arrow to try moving
    it. If nothing is blocking the path in front of its head, the arrow will slide
    out and disappear. Some arrows block other arrows. Remove the free arrows first
    to open new paths. As the board clears, more arrows become available.
